# Shopier Integration Plan

## Goal Description
Integrate **Shopier** as a payment provider to enable monetization channels for the AutonomaX platform. This allows for simple payment link generation and transaction tracking.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> We are assuming "Shopier" refers to the [Shopier Payment Gateway](https://www.shopier.com/), a popular alternative to Stripe/PayPal in certain regions. If you meant "Shopify", please reject this plan and clarify.

